msgstr "Config Version must look like 2.0004 (major.minor, Fanvil Current Config Version)."

msgid "Configure and manage Yealink/Fanvil SIP phones on your FreePBX system."
msgstr "Настройка и управление SIP-телефонами Yealink/Fanvil в FreePBX."

msgid "Configure network-specific settings by IP range (CIDR notation). Settings are applied based on the phone's IP address during provisioning."
msgstr "Настройки сети по диапазону IP (CIDR). Применяются по IP телефона при провижининге."

