msgstr "Программируемые клавиши: BLF, быстрый набор и т.д."

msgid "Create Line Key Templates in General Settings first."
msgstr "Create Line Key Templates in General Settings first."

msgid "Create named Line Key templates here for BLF and speed dial layouts. Each tab is a separate template: rename it, configure the keys, then save settings. On Edit Phone, select a template and click Apply to Line Keys to copy it into that phone; the phone is updated only after you save the phone form."
msgstr "Create named Line Key templates here for BLF and speed dial layouts. Each tab is a separate template: rename it, configure the keys, then save settings. On Edit Phone, select a template and click Apply to Line Keys to copy it into that phone; the phone is updated only after you save the phone form."

